---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Скачать — SectLauncher" description="Скачайте SectLauncher для Windows, macOS и Linux.">
  <Fragment slot="header"><Header /></Fragment>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold">Скачать</h1>
    <p class="text-neutral-300 mt-2">Выберите вашу платформу.</p>

    <div class="mt-6 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
      <a href="#" class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800 p-5 bg-neutral-900/40 hover:bg-neutral-900">
        <h3 class="font-bold">Windows</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm mt-1">.exe / .msi</p>
      </a>
      <a href="#" class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800 p-5 bg-neutral-900/40 hover:bg-neutral-900">
        <h3 class="font-bold">macOS</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm mt-1">.dmg</p>
      </a>
      <a href="#" class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-800 p-5 bg-neutral-900/40 hover:bg-neutral-900">
        <h3 class="font-bold">Linux</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-400 text-sm mt-1">.AppImage / .deb</p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 text-xs text-neutral-500">
      Публикуйте контрольные суммы SHA‑256 и ссылку на релиз GitHub для доверия.
    </div>
  </section>

  <Fragment slot="footer"><Footer /></Fragment>
</BaseLayout>


